Texmake version 0.01
====================

Texmake is a cmake-like build system for large latex projects. It's designed
to do out-of-source builds of multiple output formats from a single input
format with various different graphics as input types.

INSTALLATION

To install this module do the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    svg2pdf
    svg2eps
    directoryWatch

